\~english
Installing \freediams requires no special handling.
Download the archive that corresponds to your operating system and unpack it in
the directory of your choice.

User data (parameter, database doses) are in your home
directory. Depending on your platform:

\~
\li Linux/Unix : /home/votrenom/.\freediams
\li MacOs : /Users/votrenom/.\freediams
\li Windows : %HOMEPATH%\.\freediams

